Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.41,0:02:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's when one falls for another!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.58,0:02:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the beginning of a love story!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Cony!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,James?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.72,0:02:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is the one you're in love with?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.38,0:02:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're worrying over a crush, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cray-cray!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.47,0:02:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not there yet, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, James! You so cray cray!\NYou crack me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.15,0:02:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So who's your crush?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.41,0:02:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,An old pen pal of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He moved away when we were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen him in-person since,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but we've exchanged\Nlots of letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Exchanging letters in the modern day...\NNow that's what I call romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Michelle when he was young!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,D'aww!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He was so cute, he was doing\Nmodeling gigs and stuff as a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's also very smart!\NHe was a prodigy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He can speak five languages,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,he's good at horse-riding,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm sure he's much taller now too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, Cony!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gotta be way cuter now than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm going to be in a horse-riding contest\Nnot far from your town!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"I can't wait to see you again\Nafter all this time!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're finally going to see Michelle again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Aren't you excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"You told me you were a good cook,\Nand knew a lot about classical music..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"and that you would get scouted for idol work\Njust by walking down the street in cute clothes..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sounds like you've grown into a perfect lady!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Cony, what is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I might've stretched the truth {\i1}juuust{\i0} a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted him to think of me\Nas a perfect girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A lie's only a lie\Nbecause it's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just make your lies the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I can become a perfect girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm gonna help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No one else more qualified!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The beauty master,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the king of beauty, James!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't follow,\Nbut you're blowing me away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me, and you'll be\Na perfect lady—guaranteed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I will?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You will!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:05:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you want to be a perfect lady,\Nthe road ahead is a steep one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I will become a perfect lady\Nworthy of Michelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,First up, fashion check!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to put care into your looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you want to look\Nwhen you're with Michelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a skirt that's just perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like this skirt shrunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No it didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you gained weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Erp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna prove it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Brown, your phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Look for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Pics of Cony?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof, she's swelling up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I gained... 5 pounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I gained 15 pounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have\Nall of these pics of me anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that, Cony!\NYou've gotta get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? On what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,James' diet program!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Step 1, exercise!\NStep 2, exercise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Steps 3 and 4, exercise!\NStep 5, exercise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want Michelle\Nto think you're fat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I do this everyday,\Nand it's kept me beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How much further...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,To the other side of that mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And after this, we'll be working on thosle muscles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Move along, daylight's burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.44,0:06:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do any more of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this sweet aroma?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it what I think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We're giving out ice cream samples!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you care for a taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Samples?\NDoes that mean it's {\i1}free?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yippee, this is my lucky day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.59,0:07:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how sweet the temptation,\Nyou have to overcome it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect to hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm on a diet, so I'll have to pass!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,James!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see through...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,your every move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaat?! Aw, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get running!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You've still got a ways to go\Nto be a perfect lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Cooking class with James!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Crash course on the classics with James!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this song called?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell asleep\Nwith your eyes open?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Crash course on makeup\Nwith James!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Next, you'll be learning\Ntable manners!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! There's still more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Plenty more!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like I told you! If you want to be perfect,\Nthe road ahead is steep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Cony!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for your morning training!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do you plan on sleeping in?! Wake...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey! Get back here, Cony!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done, okay?\NI give up on being more ladylike!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Put it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It fits...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard work always pays off, Cony.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good to see you again, Cony!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looks like you've become\Na perfect lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Michelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll become more ladylike\Nfor Michelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't run away anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now give me 10 sprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:10:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Moo-moo-moon, moo-moo-moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Cony?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, hello, Moon!\NIt's good to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like a totally different person!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like a model!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Moon, you scamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is Violin Sonata No. 569\Nin G minor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! G minor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing left to teach you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Onwards, Cony!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything, James!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Off I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Michelle.\NI wonder how he'll react when he sees me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.83,0:10:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My Michelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What the?!\NWhat happened to you, Cony?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Was he gone by the time you got there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he was... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.18,0:10:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...So was his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanted his {\i1}good friend{\i0}\Nto meet her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,His good friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a girlfriend, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically, the guy dumped you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm glad she's not\Nbeating herself up over it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so full, it's making me all sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...she's already 200% less ladylike\Nthan before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Brown, what're you blushing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Moo-moo-moon, moo-moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, the moon is so beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Moon, what's the "big thing"\Nyou wanted to tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? "Seeking cute, attractive hula girls?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Moon, you could never\Npull that off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an awful dancer,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,plus you're not even a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that,\Nthe thing above it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Above that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Monster sighting."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"A suspicious shadow lurks around in the dark\Nmaking strange noises."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:13:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"Night after night it comes out,\Nplunging those who see it into pure terror..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And I saw it for myself last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Will y'all help me bust this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Bust it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... This monster put me through so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Must I live on with this regret?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to pass.\NMonsters give me the creeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here.\NNot like this is our problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What took you so long, Brown?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you coming with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna find out who this monster is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Attaboy, Brown!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,See, he gets me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Brown?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, now that we're all here,\Nlet's head to where I spot the monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this where you saw that strange shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If we poke around here,\Nwe should find some leads.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The investigation is on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Off we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you insist...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Find anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you, Brown?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No luck, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This case is shrouded in darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Cony!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Cony!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But it looks like the road ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Not quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Whatever it is must've crossed this bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:15:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means our strange shadow\Nis beyond this point!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way anyone's using this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What she said! What kind of monster\Ncould get across this old, rickety bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what makes it weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're actually making us walk on {\i1}that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not taking that risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,After me, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know what's happening anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.28,0:15:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We really should turn back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Cut it out, Moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This bridge is very sturdy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew, I'm sa—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you we should've turned back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:16:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, falling from the bridge was the right choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just some old dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And what would an old man be doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishing, duh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's even got a rod out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not foolin' me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just camouflage\Nto mask his true form.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he casted his line!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Also part of the camouflage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He caught one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Camouflage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's getting tangled up!\NWe have to save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Still camouflage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He fell in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All part of the camouflage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it isn't!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad he's safe and sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...But now we're no closer\Nto finding anything on that shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then, Plan B!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do a stakeout.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You can try,\Nbut it's never gonna show.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're tired, go ahead and rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep watch on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You clearly want me to take this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the joker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it down!\NWhat's with the games?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It was either this or sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna join in?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Brown, where're ya goin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I fell asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"We received over 1,000 hula girl applications?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still going on about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We told you already,\Nyou aren't even a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that! Above it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Above?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"There have been more sightings\Nof the shadow lurking in the dark."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It must've shown up while we were snoozing away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What took you so long, Brown?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And you just had to leave us outta nowhere last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose you saw the shadow, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He fell asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.56,0:18:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been staying up late, Brown?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What could {\i1}Brown{\i0} be doing up late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, he was up late?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't he like this yesterday too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:18:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:19:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! We stakeout again tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you wanna play tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not here to play games!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put my bed right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not here to sleep either!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If my theory is correct,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then tucking in early might be the right call.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Everyone, it's bedtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I just have to stay still and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stuffed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers to my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you dozing off for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:20:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured out who's behind the shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Moon, why are we following Brown...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He may have fooled everyone else,\Nbut he won't fool me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The shadow appeared\Nafter he went missing last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then today, he shows up looking sleepless!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like that the day before too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that Brown...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The shadow didn't even look like his, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at his backpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It carries all the tools for his monster disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you throw your friend under like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Brown's getting dressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's wearing a skirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A skirt...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear some noise...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This music is so calming...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Calming music? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.66,0:21:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nothing like the sound I heard before...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Brown?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This{\i0} is the suspicious shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're applying to be a hula girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.14,0:21:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were just getting your practice in at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder you're sleepless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.06,0:21:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then who's really behind the strange shadow...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah, wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That shadow! It has to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.16,0:21:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the strange one I saw before!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessica!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.71,0:21:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sally!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! What brings you all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you guys want to stargaze with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't suppose you two were here last night...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.43,0:22:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We were!\NThe stars look so pretty out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.93,0:22:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.97,0:22:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So the ones behind the strange shadow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.14,0:22:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...are you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What strange shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.44,0:22:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.81,0:22:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look up at the sky!\N{\i1}So many stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.07,0:22:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.74,0:22:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta make wishes!
Dialogue: 1,0:24:01.21,0:24:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Next time on {\i1}Line Town...
Dialogue: 1,0:24:02.96,0:24:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Unfortunately no fortunes for me,\Nfor fortunes aren't in my favor.{占い占わないで占わなければ占わない}
Dialogue: 1,0:24:05.72,0:24:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A forsaken fortune\Nis naught but forsaken!{売れない占い全然売れない}
Dialogue: 1,0:24:07.63,0:24:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But if I ask for my fortune,\Ndon't tell me the unfortunate!{占いたいなら占わないなんて言わないで裏だって占い}
Dialogue: 1,0:24:11.05,0:24:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Read my for-tuuune!{ならばいらららら～}
Dialogue: 1,0:24:13.06,0:24:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Unfortunately, no fortunes! For fortunately,\Nmy fortune's been forgivenly fortold!{占い占わなくね　占わなくなくなくなくなくない占い}
Dialogue: 1,0:24:16.89,0:24:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nailed it.
